Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是運動服部的鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從駕駛艙裏出來待機 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..
