Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地跑來宣戰..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殘骸啊
